Suna hain log usse aankh bhar ke dekhte hain
So uske shehr me kuch din Thehar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain rabt hain usse kharaab haalon se
So apne aap ko barbaad kar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain dard ki gahak hain chashm-e-naaz uski
So hum bhi uski gali se gujar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain usse bhi hain Sher-o-shayari se shagaf
To hum bhi mojize apni hunar ke dekhte hain

Suna hian bole toh baaton se phool zadte hain
Ye baat hain to chalo baat kar ke dekhte hain

Suna hian raat usse chand takta rehta hain
Sitaare baal-e-falak se utar ke dekhte hain

Suna hai din ko usse titliyaan satati hain
Suna hain raatko jugnoo thehar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain hashr hain uski gazaal si ankhen
Suna hain hiran usse dasht bhar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain raat se badi hai kakule uski
Suna hain shaam ko saayein thehar ke dekhte hain

Suna hai uski siyaah chashmagi kayamat hain
So usko surma farosh aah bhar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain uske labon se gulaab jalte hain
So hum bahar par iljaam dhar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain aayina timsaal hain jabi uski
Jo saada dil hai wo ban savar ke dekhte hain

Suna hai jab se himaail hain uski gardan me
Mijaaz aur hi laal o guhar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain chashm-e-tassavur se dasht-e-imka main
Palang jaaviye uski kamar ke dekhte hain

Suna hain uske badan ki tarash aisi hain
phool bhi apni kabayen katar ke dekhte hain

Wo sarv-kad hain lekin begul-e-muraad nahi
Ki uske shajar pe shaguphe samar ke dekhte hain

Ek najar se lutata hain kaafila dil ka
so usko rah-ravaan-o-tamanna bhi darr ke dekhte hain

Suna hain uske shabista se muttasil hain bahisht
maki udhar ke bhi jalve idhar ke dekhte hain

Ruke toh gardishein uska tavaaf karti hain
chale toh usko jamaane tehar ke dekhte hain

Kise naseeb ke be-paharan usse dekhe
kabhi kabhi dar-o-diwaar ghar ke dekhte hain

saab kahaniyaan hi sahi sab mubaalge hi sahi
Agar wo khwaab hain to taabir kar ke dekhte hain

Aab uske shehar me thehare ki kooch kar jaayen
Faraaz aao sitaare safar ke dekhte hain
